{"tid":519910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警隊醜聞】38歲男警涉「衰十一」 與15歲女童性交","createTime":"2018-01-05T00:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T05:28:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"741b0c82bf6b85221083faeeb2544f2f96185097","tid":519910,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T00:29:04.000Z","msg":"警隊又再爆出醜聞，38歲姓陳警員涉嫌於2013年在屯門區與當時15歲的女童發生性行為，涉嫌與年齡在16歲以下的女童非法性交，新界南總區刑事總部人員經深入調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日上午將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子已被停職，將被控以一項與年齡在16歲以下的女童非法性交罪，案件將於下周四(11日)在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180104/57666476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180104%2F57666476&d=wxO4TvblOyXzBSP4btRs8xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c6a66770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180104%2F57666476&h=bf50c246\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180104/57666476</a>"},{"pid":"c0c0386f86e746d89b2cd7ef0d3b1df1f57e5ab0","tid":519910,"uid":20177,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n有冇得省略呢句野，好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a54dc82d363e8c67c7dd8dc496c5d2869adb72","tid":519910,"uid":63944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"403cd5c165f588432d4df507bdc0cc7e8fd047e7","tid":519910,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T23:59:27.000Z","msg":"員佐級乜撚野公會有咩講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706057ca85740aaa73e70d0abded972efc1723ed","tid":